程序包 aquintos.ee.metric.temp.calc.B_Team_Dev.VCUtil

类 VCUtil.Excel_Import_Util

  • java.lang.Object
    • aquintos.ee.metric.temp.calc.B_Team_Dev.VCUtil.VCUtil.Excel_Import_Util
  • 封闭类:
    VCUtil
    public static class VCUtil.Excel_Import_Util
extends java.lang.Object
    Utility class for performing various operations related to Excel imports and ITempTable data. This class provides static methods for retrieving information from ITempTable instances and handling Excel data in the context of PREEvision attributes. Example Usage: 
     {
   @code
   // Retrieve an Excel column by name
   ITempTableColumn column = VCUtil.Excel_Import_Util.getExcelColumnByName(excelTable, "ColumnName");

   // Get the cell content of a specific row and column name
   String cellContent = VCUtil.Excel_Import_Util.getExcelCellByRowAndColumnName(tableRow, "ColumnName");

   // Get non-empty cells from a specific column in the Excel table
   List nonEmptyCells = VCUtil.Excel_Import_Util.getColumnNonEmptyCellByColumnName(excelTable, "ColumnName");
 }
